<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/samantha-dixon> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Samantha Dixon was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government on 6 September 2025. She was previously Vice-Chamberlain of HM Household (Government Whip) between 10 July 2024 and 6 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Chester North and Neston in July 2024."@en .
